The Hebrew is Shema Yisrael, which is basically the Jewish equivalent to the Lord’s Prayer in terms of it being the major prayer in religious services.

Also, you may want to remove the vowels symbols from יהוה or the entire text as a whole. Since there were no vowels in old Hebrew, it could help add an older feel to the text.





